dct_title_s: Oil and gas infrastructure in the Caspian Sea region : March 2001
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Depths shown by bathymetric isolines and gradient tints. Oilfields, gasfields, pipelines, refineries, concession areas, and tanker terminals are located. Includes directory of "Major energy companies in the Caspian Sea region." Map no: "751972AI (R02051) 3-01".
